---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Welcome to Kingson Wu's Technical Blog</h1>
			<p>
				Hello! I'm Kingson Wu, a senior software engineer exploring advanced topics in software architecture,
				distributed systems, large language models, and modern development practices.
				This blog is dedicated to sharing deep technical insights and practical experiences.
			</p>
			<p>
				Here you'll find in-depth articles on topics such as:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Large Language Models (LLMs) and AI systems</li>
				<li>Distributed systems and microservices architecture</li>
				<li>Network protocols and infrastructure</li>
				<li>Generative AI and multimodal systems</li>
				<li>Modern programming methodologies</li>
				<li>RPC systems and service communication</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Each post aims to bridge the gap between theoretical concepts and real-world applications,
				providing both analysis and practical implementation guidance.
			</p>
			<p>
				Feel free to browse through my articles, and don't hesitate to reach out if you have questions or suggestions.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
